data.description:
Embark on your journey to homeownership with an unbeatable deal, with seller concessions of $6000! This charming ranch 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, property is located on a spacious 0.9-acre lot. This home is located in a well-established neighborhood within a cul-de-sac. Located just down the road from top tier schools. Inside, appreciate the beautifully updated kitchen and bathrooms, with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Updated HVAC & ductwork replaced in 2020. Enjoy your new home with the easy of having a one-year Home Warrenty Included! Schedule a viewing today or stop by the open house this Saturday, 4/27/2024 1pm-3pm.

Disclaimer: Property is located in FEMA flood zone AE and Flood insurance is required. Property has never flooded according to current seller as well as the previous seller. Crawlspace and foundation inspection was competed, and no flood damage was found.
